videos.description: Shannon Evans II throws it to De'Quon Lake  under the basket who gets a layup.
videos.headline: ASU's Evans no-look pass leads to lay-in

videos.description: Shannon Evans II intercepts a pass and takes it all the way for an easy lay-in.
videos.headline: ASU's Evans goes coast-to-coast for steal and score

videos.description: Robert Franks kicks it out to Viont'e Daniels who swishes a triple.
videos.headline: Daniels sinks 3-pointer from corner for Wazzu

videos.description: Tra Holder drives the ball into the paint for a smooth layup.
videos.headline: ASU's Holder scores with a big-time move

videos.description: Romello White takes flight as he gets back-to-back Arizona State dunks.
videos.headline: White hammers home back-to-back dunks

videos.description: Viont'e Daniels finds Carter Skaggs, who drains a triple to tie the game at 59.
videos.headline: Cougars' Skaggs ties game with open 3-pointer

videos.description: Drick Bernstine intercepts pass which leads to Robert Franks driving the ball home for a layup.
videos.headline: Cougars with a clutch steal and score

videos.description: Tra Holder intercepts a pass and takes it to the rim for a nice layup as Arizona State goes on to beat Washington State 88-78.
videos.headline: ASU's Holder with steal-and-score
